	</div></center>
	<center><div class="row">
 	 	<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			<p><b>Step 10)</b>  Fold the bottom of the paper behind the model.</p>
 		</div>
  		<div class="column" style="background-color:white;">
    			 <p><b>The complete sparrow</b></p>
 		</div>
	</div></center>
